---
title: Curriculum
layout: layout.njk
css: curriculum
heroImage: /assets/images/curriculum-hero.png
---

<section class="curriculum-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="curriculum-features">
      <div class="curriculum-feature-card">
        <div class="curriculum-feature-header">
          <h3>Standards-Aligned</h3>
          <div class="curriculum-feature-icon curriculum-feature-icon--green">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00A63E" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>Our curriculum follows Portuguese Ministry of Education standards while being adapted for students in Canada.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="curriculum-feature-card">
        <div class="curriculum-feature-header">
          <h3>Age-Appropriate</h3>
          <div class="curriculum-feature-icon curriculum-feature-icon--red">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E7000B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="8" y2="12"/><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="16" y2="16"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>Each level is carefully designed to match the developmental stage and learning capabilities of students.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="curriculum-feature-card">
        <div class="curriculum-feature-header">
          <h3>Comprehensive</h3>
          <div class="curriculum-feature-icon curriculum-feature-icon--blue">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#155DFC" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>Beyond language, we teach history, literature, and help students connect with Portuguese culture.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="curriculum-levels">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="curriculum-tabs">
      {% for slug, level in curriculum %}
        <button class="curriculum-tab{% if loop.first %} curriculum-tab--active{% endif %}" data-tab="{{ slug }}">{{ level.tab }}</button>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% for slug, level in curriculum %}
      <div class="curriculum-detail{% if not loop.first %} curriculum-detail--hidden{% endif %}" data-panel="{{ slug }}">
        <div class="curriculum-detail-header">
          <div>
            <h2>{{ level.title }}</h2>
            <p class="curriculum-detail-age">{{ level.ages }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="curriculum-detail-intro">{{ level.intro }}</p>
        <div class="curriculum-detail-columns">
          <div class="curriculum-detail-column">
            <h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              Learning Objectives
            </h3>
            <ul class="curriculum-checklist">
              {% for item in level.objectives %}
                <li>{{ item }}</li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="curriculum-detail-column">
            <h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="8" y2="12"/><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="16" y2="16"/></svg>
              Topics Covered
            </h3>
            <ul class="curriculum-bullet-list">
              {% for item in level.topics %}
                <li>{{ item }}</li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="curriculum-fees">
  <div class="container curriculum-fees-grid">
    <div class="curriculum-fees-image">
      <img src="/assets/images/curriculum-fees.png" alt="Students in classroom" />
    </div>
    <div class="curriculum-fees-content">
      <h2>School Fees</h2>
      <ul class="curriculum-fees-pricing">
        <li>One child $500/year</li>
        <li>Two siblings $850/year</li>
        <li>Three siblings $1000/year</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="curriculum-fees-payment">
        <p>Families may choose to pay tuition in one full payment or in two installments.</p>
        <h4>1. One Full Payment</h4>
        <p><strong>E-transfer</strong> – due on November 30 to {{ site.email.payments }}</p>
        <p><strong>Cheque</strong> – due on November 30</p>
        <p><strong>Cash</strong> – due on November 30</p>
        <h4>2. Two Installments</h4>
        <p><strong>E-transfer</strong> – 1st installment due November 30 / 2nd installment due January 31 to {{ site.email.payments }}</p>
        <p><strong>Post-dated cheques</strong> – 1st installment dated November 30 / 2nd installment dated January 31</p>
        <p><strong>Cash</strong> – 1st installment due November 30 / 2nd installment due January 31</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-cta">
  <div class="home-cta-bg">
    <img src="/assets/images/cta-bg.png" alt="" />
  </div>
  <div class="home-cta-content">
    <h2>{{ home.cta.heading }}</h2>
    <p>{{ home.cta.body }}</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">REGISTER NOW</a>
  </div>
</section>
